Cravings for Milk Tea during this Extended Circuit Breaker? @hausbrew.sg got you covered. You can now order ready to drink Haus Brew Premium Selection of Milk Teas and Fruit Tea Series at the comfort of your home and just sip away!

Haus Brew takes pride with their selection of premium Earl Grey Tea leaves and high quality milk creamer to produce the best quality taste of their Milk Teas. They use delicate and masterful brewing process to a rich and flavourful taste in every bottle. Haus Brew also seeks perfection in every brewing process to achieve authentic infusion of flavours.
.
📢 Haus Brew Promotion
🥤At just $45.90 for 22 bottles (11 Flavours x 2 Bottles Each)
🥤Includes a personalized note (if you are ordering it as a gift, key under "Remarks")
🥤Free Haus Brew Cooler Bag
🥤Free delivery to your doorstep.
.
You can order via:
🌿 WhatsApp at https://wa.me/6591785310
🌿 Online at https://gourmetsupplies.com.sg/home/532-haus-brew-milk-and-fruit-tea.html

You can also include a personalized note if you're getting it as a gift, perfect to brighten up someone's day during this CB period!

Thank you so much @hausbrew.sg for sending these awesome drinks!
.
